  4005-HID-apple-Add-support-for-MacBookPro15-4-keyboard-tr.patch
  4006-HID-apple-Add-support-for-MacBookPro16-2-keyboard-tr.patch
  4007-HID-apple-Add-support-for-MacBookAir9-1-keyboard-tra.patch
